trans-unit.source: Represents a <xref:System.DateTime> property (and its value) of a printing system hardware or software component.
trans-unit.target: 表示<xref:System.DateTime>属性 （和其值） 的打印系统硬件或软件组件。</xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintDateTimeProperty"></xref> class for the specified property.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新实例<xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintDateTimeProperty"></xref>的指定属性的类。

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.DateTime> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: `attributeName`应拼写的某些特定的名称完全相同<xref:System.DateTime>打印系统对象，包括大小写的属性。</xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.StartTimeOfDay%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> object must be spelled "StartTimeOfDay", not "StartTime" or "Starttimeofday".
trans-unit.target: 例如，<xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.StartTimeOfDay%2A>属性<xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo>"StartTimeOfDay"、 不是"StartTime"或"Starttimeofday"必须拼写对象。</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> </xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.StartTimeOfDay%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name of the <xref:System.DateTime> property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintDateTimeProperty"></xref> represents.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintDateTimeProperty"></xref> class that has the specified value for the specified attribute.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新实例<xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintDateTimeProperty"></xref>具有指定的属性的指定的值的类。

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.DateTime> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: `attributeName`应拼写的某些特定的名称完全相同<xref:System.DateTime>打印系统对象，包括大小写的属性。</xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.StartTimeOfDay%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> object must be spelled "StartTimeOfDay", not "StartTime" or "Starttimeofday".
trans-unit.target: 例如，<xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.StartTimeOfDay%2A>属性<xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo>"StartTimeOfDay"、 不是"StartTime"或"Starttimeofday"必须拼写对象。</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> </xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.StartTimeOfDay%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name of the <xref:System.DateTime> property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintDateTimeProperty"></xref> represents.
The value of the property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintDateTimeProperty"></xref> represents.
Gets or sets the value of the property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintDateTimeProperty"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置属性的值<xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintDateTimeProperty"></xref>表示。
